{
  "stem": "628.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I looked into the gas chambers when they were working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Today, I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, that's-- [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Serge ?] also said to me is that-- I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because when I went with the group from the Belgian television, and I said that I go in there, and I was not found out, so that it must be-- I must be-- God must have-- somebody was with me.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that Sonderkommando-- he-- he's not alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After three months, they killed him as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because I spoke with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was in contact with then, even when they went out the gates.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I never-- but that moment, where they had that talk about gassing the people quicker, and I moved around there, they didn't see me-- quick in and out, [INAUDIBLE] that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I went back to the barracks with the band.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Rabetzki, the biggest sadist-- he used to hit me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Oh, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He gave me-- when we came into the camp, he said, Berliner, come here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Here is a box of chocolate for you, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You whistled in front of the marvelous-- in front of the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Suddenly-- so my life went on in D lager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And in the evening, when the barracks were closed, that was-- you see, in these-- in these camps, the SS had everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The-- they had their own tailor shop there, the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "All the uniforms the SS used was made to measure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "All the boots they had-- they had the most beautiful boots maker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Some, they didn't gas those people they-- they needed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Jewelry-- the ones who made jewelry, the ones expert you have to check the diamonds-- probably, they-- they were all gassed after a time.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
